data.description: Discover the charm of this 3 bed, 2.5 bath home at 1423 Butler Dr, spanning 2190 sq ft. The residence features wood flooring and tile throughout the downstairs area, enhancing its warm, inviting ambiance. The living space is perfect for both relaxing and entertaining. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Outside, a serene backyard offers a peaceful retreat. Conveniently located in between Potranco and Loop 410, this home combines space and comfort in a prime setting.
